Formulas, Row Group Dragging, Absolute Sorting, Column Selection, Filtering & Export Overlays.

## What's New

AG Grid {% migrationVersion() %} adds important new features – [Formulas](./formulas), [Row Group Dragging](./grouping-row-dragging), [Absolute Sorting](./row-sorting/#absolute-sorting), [Column Selection](./cell-selection/#selecting-cells-via-column-headers), [Filtering & Export Overlays](./overlays-overview/), as described in the [release post](https://blog.ag-grid.com/whats-new-in-ag-grid-35/).

